name: Taleam Systems
overview: We are an information technology company providing computer repair, service and support to residences and small and medium businesses in the Ottawa-Gatineau area. We offer: computer repair, virus and spyware removal, printer and scanner setup, wireless network setup and installation, hardware upgrades, computer training, data backups and complete IT solutions. We can bring the solution to you, onsite, by phone or remote support via Internet, to restore your PC health and optimize performance. Taleam Systems is dedicated to offering the most friendly, reliable, honest service and support to our customers in the Ottawa-Gatineau area. Whether you need a new motherboard, have driver issues, need your computer repaired, have MS Outlook difficulties, are receiving error messages or have technical issues with a laptop or desktop, Taleam Systems is your one-stop shop for computer products and service, including support for Dell, HP, IBM, Intel and Lenovo products.
